      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 12:19",
      "text": "ܐܠܘ ܕܝܢ ܟܠܗܘܢ ܚܕ ܗܘܘ ܗܕܡܐ ܐܝܟܐ ܗܘܐ ܦܓܪܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.12.20",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 12:20",
      "text": "ܗܫܐ ܕܝܢ ܗܕܡܐ ܐܝܬܝܗܘܢ ܤܓܝܐܐ ܚܕ ܗܘ ܕܝܢ ܦܓܪܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
